## Practical Learning Approach

Instead of just watching or reading:

Flow followed:
```
Watch → Pause → Test → Fail → Retry
```

Why this matters:
- Errors show how the backend behaves
- Failures reveal incorrect assumptions
- Repetition builds pattern recognition

